  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1158">
<l>iṉṉātu iṉaṉillūr vāḻta lataṉiṉum </l>
<l>iṉṉā tiṉiyārp pirivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Painful is it to live in a friendless town; but far more painful is it to part from one's lover.</l>
            </lg>
